♪May stars guide us through rough waves♪

4
00:00:23,420 --> 00:00:28,520
♪I give all my love unreservedly♪

5
00:00:29,030 --> 00:00:30,900
♪May transient frost♪

6
00:00:31,020 --> 00:00:34,690
♪Persist through obstacles for love♪

7
00:00:34,820 --> 00:00:40,330
♪I wait for you to look back
in this rocky life♪

8
00:00:40,650 --> 00:00:42,550
♪I can stay for the promise♪

9
00:00:42,670 --> 00:00:46,180
♪Despite seasons recur♪

10
00:00:46,380 --> 00:00:51,760
♪The love deep within
will transcend time♪

11
00:00:51,760 --> 00:00:57,500
[Secrets of the Shadow Sect]

12
00:00:57,540 --> 00:01:00,820
[Episode 3]

13
00:01:16,380 --> 00:01:17,300
Please calm down, Master.

14
00:01:17,420 --> 00:01:18,220
Calm down?

15
00:01:19,500 --> 00:01:21,620
My shadow guard defies my order.

16
00:01:22,220 --> 00:01:23,580
How do I calm myself,

17
00:01:23,860 --> 00:01:24,980
pray tell?

18
00:01:26,180 --> 00:01:27,060
She has a child.

19
00:01:27,180 --> 00:01:28,500
So what?

20
00:01:28,900 --> 00:01:30,660
Do you know what kind of place
Lingtian Palace is?

21
00:01:31,220 --> 00:01:32,020
In this place,

22
00:01:32,540 --> 00:01:34,100
the strong hold sway

23
00:01:34,380 --> 00:01:35,820
over the insignificant lives of
the weak.

24
00:01:36,060 --> 00:01:37,500
It's just a human life.

25
00:01:37,700 --> 00:01:38,820
Who would care?

26
00:01:40,180 --> 00:01:41,100
If so,

27
00:01:41,820 --> 00:01:42,780
my sister and I

28
00:01:42,780 --> 00:01:44,020
were also deserted

29
00:01:44,100 --> 00:01:45,060
and insignificant.

30
00:01:45,820 --> 00:01:47,460
Why did you save us?

31
00:01:50,620 --> 00:01:51,380
Master,

32
00:01:51,940 --> 00:01:53,580
I don't show mercy on others

33
00:01:53,860 --> 00:01:55,300
nor on that woman.

34
00:01:55,980 --> 00:01:57,260
I just thought

35
00:01:57,900 --> 00:01:59,060
that it wasn't your intention

36
00:01:59,500 --> 00:02:00,460
to kill innocent lives.

37
00:02:00,580 --> 00:02:01,380
Yingshi.

38
00:02:04,700 --> 00:02:06,100
Are you teaching me a lesson?

39
00:02:06,220 --> 00:02:07,100
I wouldn't dare.

40
00:02:07,100 --> 00:02:08,220
You wouldn't?

41
00:02:09,420 --> 00:02:10,740
But it seems to me

42
00:02:10,740 --> 00:02:11,980
you behave otherwise.

43
00:02:13,620 --> 00:02:14,420
Come.

44
00:02:18,020 --> 00:02:18,860
Young Master.

45
00:02:19,220 --> 00:02:20,780
Yingshi defied my order.

46
00:02:20,820 --> 00:02:21,620
Take him away

47
00:02:22,260 --> 00:02:23,100
and punish him with thirty lashes

48
00:02:23,260 --> 00:02:24,420
to set an example.

49
00:02:44,780 --> 00:02:46,860
Male escorts are deemed lowly here

50
00:02:47,020 --> 00:02:48,380
and aren't qualified
to enter the Hall of Discipline.

51
00:02:48,660 --> 00:02:50,020
Remove your clothes.

52
00:03:04,540 --> 00:03:05,620
I heard that Young Master

53
00:03:05,620 --> 00:03:06,660
took someone in yesterday.

54
00:03:06,900 --> 00:03:08,380
Why does she punish the newcomer today?

55
00:03:08,700 --> 00:03:10,580
Why does he dress like a guard?

56
00:03:11,860 --> 00:03:13,420
Perhaps he intentionally
wore that clothes

57
00:03:13,660 --> 00:03:15,420
and tried to please
the Young Palace Master,

58
00:03:15,460 --> 00:03:16,620
but it backfired

59
00:03:16,620 --> 00:03:17,620
and annoyed her.

60
00:03:31,460 --> 00:03:33,020
After all, he is an elite

61
00:03:33,020 --> 00:03:34,100
trained for ten years
in the Shadow Sect.

62
00:03:34,820 --> 00:03:37,020
Young Master,
since you have become his master,

63
00:03:37,260 --> 00:03:38,660
why did you punish him

64
00:03:38,660 --> 00:03:39,660
using the rules of male escorts?

65
00:03:40,020 --> 00:03:41,620
Isn't that too humiliating?

66
00:03:43,260 --> 00:03:44,740
Humiliating?

67
00:03:45,540 --> 00:03:46,860
What he has suffered in the Shadow Sect

68
00:03:47,100 --> 00:03:48,220
in the past ten years

69
00:03:48,220 --> 00:03:49,420
is more than this.

70
00:03:50,260 --> 00:03:51,060
Yes.

71
00:03:52,900 --> 00:03:54,340
Speaking of which,

72
00:03:54,860 --> 00:03:56,620
he is quite smart.

73
00:03:57,140 --> 00:03:58,380
We couldn't make

74
00:03:58,380 --> 00:03:59,500
the Pipa player talk,

75
00:04:00,060 --> 00:04:01,340
but he made it.

76
00:04:02,860 --> 00:04:04,620
He's the shadow guard of First Class.

77
00:04:05,260 --> 00:04:06,780
There are only a small number

78
00:04:07,260 --> 00:04:08,820
who graduated as First Class
in the Shadow Sect in the past ten years.

79
00:04:10,300 --> 00:04:11,860
Last night's mission

80
00:04:11,860 --> 00:04:13,140
shows that he is a person

81
00:04:13,140 --> 00:04:14,500
with a conscience.

82
00:04:15,420 --> 00:04:17,140
If you would recruit him,

83
00:04:17,300 --> 00:04:19,140
he can be of a great help to us.

84
00:04:22,340 --> 00:04:23,340
But he said

85
00:04:23,340 --> 00:04:24,740
it wasn't my intention.

86
00:04:25,460 --> 00:04:26,660
This is truly

87
00:04:27,420 --> 00:04:28,620
hilarious.

88
00:04:30,860 --> 00:04:31,740
Young Master.

89
00:04:31,740 --> 00:04:32,860
Second Young Master is here.

90
00:04:46,420 --> 00:04:47,860
Greetings, Second Young Master.

91
00:04:49,540 --> 00:04:50,740
Last year, my sister said

92
00:04:50,740 --> 00:04:52,260
the tea was tasteless.

93
00:04:52,340 --> 00:04:52,860
Now

94
00:04:53,100 --> 00:04:55,020
is a good season for growing tea leaves.

95
00:04:55,140 --> 00:04:55,860
I specially...

96
00:04:55,860 --> 00:04:57,020
Second Young Master,
that's very kind of you.

97
00:04:57,500 --> 00:04:59,020
It's just that you came
at the wrong time.

98
00:04:59,060 --> 00:05:00,780
Young Master instructed

99
00:05:00,780 --> 00:05:01,900
that she wouldn't receive visitors
today.

100
00:05:05,260 --> 00:05:06,500
I have come here ten times,

101
00:05:06,500 --> 00:05:07,620
but there are eight times
I couldn't meet

102
00:05:07,620 --> 00:05:08,420
her.

103
00:05:08,820 --> 00:05:09,620
Forget it.

104
00:05:13,460 --> 00:05:14,860
Please give this to Xuan.

105
00:05:15,660 --> 00:05:16,180
Yes.

106
00:05:16,620 --> 00:05:17,660
I thank you

107
00:05:17,660 --> 00:05:18,820
on behalf of Young Master.

108
00:05:50,140 --> 00:05:51,260
It's him. Come with me.

109
00:05:53,180 --> 00:05:54,380
I thought the newcomer

110
00:05:54,380 --> 00:05:55,460
had a gorgeous face.

111
00:05:55,660 --> 00:05:57,780
Yet Young Master has already lost
interest in him.

112
00:05:57,980 --> 00:05:59,780
Nothing is special about him.

113
00:06:02,220 --> 00:06:04,220
He got whipped
after failing to please Young Master.

114
00:06:04,580 --> 00:06:06,260
He should behave now.

115
00:06:12,860 --> 00:06:13,340
Master.

116
00:06:13,340 --> 00:06:14,460
[Lingtian Palace]

117
00:06:14,460 --> 00:06:15,740
As far as I know,

118
00:06:15,740 --> 00:06:16,820
the Wanxin Manual

119
00:06:16,820 --> 00:06:18,940
can help boost one's inner strength
within a short time.

120
00:06:19,540 --> 00:06:20,700
If Young Master

121
00:06:20,700 --> 00:06:23,260
has acquired it,

122
00:06:23,580 --> 00:06:25,180
why didn't you notice anything

123
00:06:25,180 --> 00:06:26,380
when you tested her

124
00:06:26,860 --> 00:06:28,660
for multiple times?

125
00:06:30,380 --> 00:06:31,540
Over the years,

126
00:06:32,220 --> 00:06:32,940
Xuan

127
00:06:33,380 --> 00:06:34,780
has never shown

128
00:06:34,780 --> 00:06:37,220
any martial arts skills
other than our own sect.

129
00:06:38,780 --> 00:06:40,580
Still, I could sense

130
00:06:41,060 --> 00:06:42,380
that she has hidden many things

131
00:06:43,180 --> 00:06:45,380
from me.

132
00:06:46,060 --> 00:06:46,980
Master.

133
00:06:47,980 --> 00:06:49,340
I believe

134
00:06:50,260 --> 00:06:51,580
there is no flawless disguise

135
00:06:51,580 --> 00:06:53,180
in this world.

136
00:06:54,180 --> 00:06:55,260
Perhaps you should

137
00:06:55,780 --> 00:06:57,540
often remind her

138
00:06:57,540 --> 00:06:58,780
to practice martial arts.

139
00:07:09,620 --> 00:07:11,300
Tonight, Master Ling will summon
Young Master.

140
00:07:11,460 --> 00:07:12,740
When she leaves for the main hall,

141
00:07:12,740 --> 00:07:14,260
Mr. Ya will tag along,

142
00:07:14,260 --> 00:07:15,940
leaving the Xuantian House unguarded.

143
00:07:16,060 --> 00:07:17,460
Seize the time and go for your mission.

144
00:07:18,140 --> 00:07:19,100
All right.

145
00:07:58,040 --> 00:07:59,420
Where is Yingshi's place?

146
00:08:00,060 --> 00:08:01,700
His room is at the southernmost corner.

147
00:08:01,900 --> 00:08:03,620
We haven't got the measure of him yet.

148
00:08:03,860 --> 00:08:05,180
Mr. Ya and I think

149
00:08:05,180 --> 00:08:07,140
it's best to keep him away from you.

150
00:08:09,500 --> 00:08:10,540
The Shadow Sect

151
00:08:10,860 --> 00:08:12,060
is a place surrounded
by a pack of jackals.

152
00:08:12,260 --> 00:08:14,500
But he adheres to the promise
made ten years ago

153
00:08:14,500 --> 00:08:16,140
and fights his way out to come for me.

154
00:08:16,620 --> 00:08:18,740
The way he acts
is also different from others.

155
00:08:21,300 --> 00:08:22,900
This guy is interesting.

156
00:08:23,420 --> 00:08:24,620
Let's go and see him.

157
00:08:38,420 --> 00:08:41,740
♪If hand waves are
the prelude to farewell♪

158
00:08:42,180 --> 00:08:45,340
♪If words hold no intention to stall♪

159
00:08:45,900 --> 00:08:47,620
♪Goodbye♪

160
00:08:47,820 --> 00:08:51,660
♪Should be reserved
for when our lives are at stake♪

161
00:08:52,940 --> 00:08:56,270
♪If time rushes swiftly
like wind and dust♪

162
00:08:56,660 --> 00:08:59,980
♪If tears come before words
after waking up♪

163
00:09:00,380 --> 00:09:02,660
♪May you not be drowned in bitterness♪

164
00:09:02,980 --> 00:09:04,260
♪I only wish your eyes♪

165
00:09:04,420 --> 00:09:07,340
♪As pure as snow♪
